(36, 1, '2012-08-06 17:42:21', '2012-08-06 17:42:21', '<p>\r\nPlease complete the form on the scholarship page to enter. Before entering, applicants are encouraged to learn more about University Bound.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>Who can participate?</h4>\r\n<p>\r\nThe contest is open to any U.S. citizen that is, or will be, pursuing a two or four-year college degree. Employees of University Bound, Inc. are not eligible to enter.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>Prize:</h4>\r\n<p>\r\nOne grand prize of $2,500 USD will be awarded directly to the winner''s school of choice, to assist with tuition and fees. Upon selection, the winning applicant''s status as an enrolled student must be verified before any prize money can be awarded.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>Submission Deadlines:</h4>\r\n<p>\r\nSubmissions will be accepted through July 31, 2012. A winner will be announced after this date, on a date that is yet to be determined.\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>Sponsor Schools:</h4>\r\n<p>\r\nDuring the entry process, University Bound will offer the opportunity to learn more about some of its sponsor schools. As clearly stated, scholarship applicants are not required to request information from these partner schools, nor will doing so increase their chances of winning. To opt-out of these offers, simply click the "Skip this offer" button at the top right of the page.\r\n</p>', 'Entry Rules', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'entry-rules', '', '', '2012-08-06 17:42:21', '2012-08-06 17:42:21', '', 0, 'http://beta.university-bound.com/?page_id=36', 0, 'page', '', 0),
